title: Customer Queue Management System
description: A queue system that prioritizes customers based on their state (e.g., Regular or Priority). It manages customer order, serving, and insertion using a custom doubly-ended queue structure.

title: Binary Tree Implementation
description: This project is a simple web-based application that allows users to create, edit, search, and visualize a Binary Tree interactively.

title: Dictionary BST
description: A binary search tree implementation for dictionary words. Users can add, search, delete, and view all words in the tree.
